    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it's a total dream. This car is in stunning, mint condition\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept and pampered its whole life, so it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a scratch or a smudge to be found. It drives like a beauty and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see this one in person to believe how perfect it is!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
