      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated masterpiece utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS stepless valve timing system to achieve a 100hp/liter output. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This specimen is mechanically flawless: the vulnerable rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced preventatively with ACL race bearings and ARP hardware. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with zero bushing deflection, and the chassis remains rigid. Finished in an impeccable Carbon Black, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no evidence of oxidation or clear-coat failure. A true collector-spec vehicle with zero deferred maintenance.",
